OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778591472
OL,3,C'I feel quite emotional': PCOS renamed
OL,4,Cto improve diagnosis and care
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Lucy
OL,7,FFitzsimons
OL,9,FA new name for polycystic ovary
OL,10,Fsyndrome (PCOS) has been announced as
OL,11,Fpart of a global initiative to improve
OL,12,Fdiagnosis and treatment.
OL,14,FAfter a 14-year-long process, it will
OL,15,Fnow be called polyendocrine metabolic
OL,16,Fovarian syndrome (PMOS).
OL,18,FThe new name, published in The Lancet
OL,19,Fmedical journal on Tuesday, was
OL,20,Fdecided after a global collaboration
OL,21,Fbetween experts and women with PMOS.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
