OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778591472
OL,3,C'I feel quite emotional': PCOS renamed
OL,4,Cto improve diagnosis and care
OL,6,FIt's been celebrated by the experts
OL,7,Fand charities involved in the process,
OL,8,Fwho hope it will improve diagnosis and
OL,9,Fattract more funding and research into
OL,10,Fthe condition.
OL,12,FThey say the new name is "reflective
OL,13,Fof the fact that it's an endocrine
OL,14,Fcondition with metabolic
OL,15,Fconsequences", instead of the main
OL,16,Ffocus being on the reproductive
OL,17,Faspects.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
