OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778591472
OL,3,C'I feel quite emotional': PCOS renamed
OL,4,Cto improve diagnosis and care
OL,6,FIt comes after a report by the PCOS
OL,7,FAll-Party Parliamentary Group last
OL,8,Fyear found that women face prolonged
OL,9,Fdelays in diagnosis, fragmented care,
OL,10,Fand limited access to treatments.
OL,12,FThe new name will be fully implemented
OL,13,Fin 2028 when the International
OL,14,FGuidelines are updated.
OL,16,FWhat is PMOS?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
