OL,3,C'I feel quite emotional': PCOS renamed
OL,4,Cto improve diagnosis and care
OL,6,FPMOS is a complex, lifelong hormonal
OL,7,Fcondition that affects one in eight
OL,8,Fwomen in the UK, which can impact
OL,9,Ftheir reproductive, metabolic, and
OL,10,Fmental health.
OL,12,FCommon symptoms of PMOS include
OL,13,Firregular or absent periods, acne,
OL,14,Fweight gain, and both excessive hair
OL,15,Fgrowth and hair loss.
OL,17,FIt also carries an increased risk of
OL,18,Flonger-term health problems, including
OL,19,Ftype 2 diabetes, endometrial cancer
OL,20,Fand cardiovascular disease.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
