OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778591472
OL,3,C'I feel quite emotional': PCOS renamed
OL,4,Cto improve diagnosis and care
OL,6,FWhy has the name changed?
OL,8,FThe previous name reduced the
OL,9,Fcomplexity of the condition by mainly
OL,10,Ffocusing on cysts and the ovaries,
OL,11,Fwhich experts say contributed to
OL,12,Fmissed diagnoses and inadequate
OL,13,Ftreatment.
OL,15,FCardiff University Professor Aled Rees
OL,16,Fwas involved in the name change
OL,17,Fprocess and said the former name
OL,18,F"lacks scientific accuracy".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
