PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778591472
OL,3,C'I feel quite emotional': PCOS renamed
OL,4,Cto improve diagnosis and care
OL,6,F"Delayed diagnosis is very common, but
OL,7,Falso people feel that the symptoms are
OL,8,Foften dismissed," he said.
OL,10,F"It's common for women living with
OL,11,FPCOS to be told you've got this
OL,12,Fdiagnosis, now come back when you want
OL,13,Fto have a baby. It puts all the
OL,14,Femphasis on the fertility
OL,15,Fconsequences."
OL,17,F"And PMOS, as we're going to change
OL,18,Fthe name, is reflective of the fact
OL,19,Fthat it's an endocrine condition with
OL,20,Fmetabolic consequences and a number of
OL,21,Fconsequences for long-term health."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778591472
OL,3,C'I feel quite emotional': PCOS renamed
OL,4,Cto improve diagnosis and care
OL,6,FImportantly, Professor Aled said there
OL,7,Fis no increased risk of cysts for
OL,8,Fwomen with PMOS.
OL,10,F"It's not cysts that are actually
OL,11,Fdeveloping in the ovary. And that's a
OL,12,Fvery common misconception.
OL,14,F"So changing awareness, improving
OL,15,Feducation, will hopefully improve the
OL,16,Fdiagnostic experience."
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
