OL,3,C'I feel quite emotional': PCOS renamed
OL,4,Cto improve diagnosis and care
OL,6,FHow will the new name help patients?
OL,8,FRachel Morman, Chair of the PMOS
OL,9,Fcharity Verity, said she feels
OL,10,F"overwhelmed" and "quite emotional
OL,11,Fthat it's actually happened".
OL,13,F"The new name is very validating from
OL,14,Fa patient perspective because they're
OL,15,Fso often dismissed and told that it's
OL,16,Fjust their periods.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778591472
OL,3,C'I feel quite emotional': PCOS renamed
OL,4,Cto improve diagnosis and care
OL,6,F"But now, actually, there's
OL,7,Frecognition that they might have an
OL,8,Fincreased risk of diabetes or
OL,9,Fsomething is affecting their whole
OL,10,Fbody."
OL,12,F"I am overwhelmed": Rachel Morman,
OL,13,Ffrom the PMOS charity Verity, speaks
OL,14,Fto ITV News about the name change
OL,16,FShe continued: "We are expecting that
OL,17,Fit will help people get a proper
OL,18,Fdiagnosis for PCOS.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778591472
OL,3,C'I feel quite emotional': PCOS renamed
OL,4,Cto improve diagnosis and care
OL,6,F"We're hoping that this will attract
OL,7,Fresearchers into the field to be
OL,8,Fexcited to look at such a complex
OL,9,Fcondition that the previous name just
OL,10,Fdidn't reflect."
OL,12,FHowever, Rachel cautioned that change
OL,13,Fwill "not happen immediately and
OL,14,Fovernight".
OL,16,F"It will be some time before it's
OL,17,Factually widely adopted, before it's
OL,18,Fwritten into UK guidance."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
