PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778591472
OL,3,C'I feel quite emotional': PCOS renamed
OL,4,Cto improve diagnosis and care
OL,6,FShe added: "It's not going to do the
OL,7,Fjob on its own. There are other things
OL,8,Fthat need to happen, such as
OL,9,Fguidelines and pathways and coding.
OL,11,F"All of these things will kind of
OL,12,Fladder up into real change."
OL,14,FProfessor Aled also said a key aspect
OL,15,Fof the name change will address
OL,16,Fcultural issues and stigma.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778591472
OL,3,C'I feel quite emotional': PCOS renamed
OL,4,Cto improve diagnosis and care
OL,6,F"In many societies, having a name that
OL,7,Fhas a focus on reproductive has
OL,8,Fconnotations for that individual
OL,9,Fbecause of the potential stigmatising
OL,10,Feffect on fertility, for example," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FWhat have patients said?
OL,15,FSunila Siddiqui, who was diagnosed
OL,16,Fwith PMOS in 2009, said she is "very
OL,17,Fdelighted" about the new name.
OL,19,FSunila told ITV News she mainly has
OL,20,Fendocrine and metabolic symptoms,
OL,21,Fincluding hirsutism and weight gain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778591472
OL,3,C'I feel quite emotional': PCOS renamed
OL,4,Cto improve diagnosis and care
OL,6,F"When I look back, if I had the
OL,7,Finformation that I have now, I would
OL,8,Fhave dealt with my symptoms and would
OL,9,Fhave been able to advocate for myself
OL,10,Fmuch better.
OL,12,F"But I'm hopeful for the girls who
OL,13,Fhave symptoms and will be diagnosed
OL,14,Fwith PCOS, or PMOS now, will be able
OL,15,Fto articulate to their GP and doctors
OL,16,Fabout how they are feeling, because
OL,17,Fthey cannot get disregarded based on
OL,18,Fthe endocrine and metabolic symptoms,
OL,19,Fbecause that is inclusive in the name
OL,20,Fnow."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
